---
title: Spring Asparagus & Shrimp Risotto with Meyer Lemon
description: The Meyer lemon is a hybrid citrus fruit - taking both the refreshing and tangy character of the lemon, and the sweet flavor of the orange. It's the perfect match for the Spring flavors in this risotto!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5512a9e56ced6e37098b456a.jpg
